{"tid":1990230,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"財經事務及庫務局政治助理楊寶蓮辭職","createTime":"2020-04-26T13:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T13:55:12.000Z","uid":20933,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"331d96a337e627ac12ae4e57d0de95893b4af21a","tid":1990230,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T13:54:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200426/s00001/232d729d9fc73985df25174c0e867e05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200426%2Fs00001%2F232d729d9fc73985df25174c0e867e05.jpg&h=d26e713b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新任財經事務及庫務局長許正宇上任不足一星期，其政治助理、2003年會考10A狀元楊寶蓮辭職。楊寶蓮今晚（26日）在社交網站facebook發文表示，能夠任政治助理是榮幸，「我認為現在是適當的時候離開」，接下來的時間會稍作休息。本報曾致電楊寶蓮，但未聯絡上。"},{"pid":"928882d1b7f8c9e73d9b99685373504278ac9be4","tid":1990230,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T13:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}